msgstr "الأقسام ومكاتب الاستراتيجية والمؤسسات الديمقراطية"

#: app/templates/platform.html:864
msgid ""
"Run deliberative polling at national or regional scale. Map what the "
"population agrees on, where genuine divisions lie, and what bridges opposing"
" views. Get structured evidence to inform policy — not just percentages, but"
