#: app/templates/briefing/landing.html:931
msgid ""
"Ministers from seven nations backed a voluntary disclosure standard for "
"frontier AI models, with Deutsche Welle and France24 noting that the EU, US,"
" and Japan have materially different implementation timelines..."
