#: app/templates/briefing/landing.html:1259
msgid ""
"We started Society Speaks to help citizens and communities find common "
"ground through structured public participation. That work revealed a bigger "
"problem: the people trying to understand society — researchers, analysts, "
"policy wonks — are drowning in information."
msgstr ""
"بدأنا Society Speaks لمساعدة المواطنين والمجتمعات على إيجاد أرضية مشتركة من "
"خلال المشاركة العامة المنظمة. أظهر هذا العمل مشكلة أكبر: الأشخاص الذين "
"يحاولون فهم المجتمع — الباحثون والمحللون وصانعو السياسات — يغرقون في "
"المعلومات."

#: app/templates/briefing/landing.html:1262
msgid ""
"Personal Briefs exists to solve that. It also <strong class=\"text-"
"white\">funds the rest of Society Speaks — civic tech that anyone, anywhere,"
" can use for free</strong>."
msgstr ""
"Personal Briefs موجود لحل هذا. كما أنه <strong class=\"text-white\">يمول "
"بقية Society Speaks — تكنولوجيا مدنية يمكن لأي شخص في أي مكان استخدامها "
"مجاناً</strong>."

#: app/templates/briefing/landing.html:1265
msgid ""
"Every paid subscription keeps our open source platform running and free: a "
"free Daily Brief for thousands of readers, deliberation tools councils and "
"NGOs use to run real public consultations, and bridge-finding algorithms "
"that show where people actually agree."
