msgid "Enforcement"
msgstr "الإنفاذ"

#: app/templates/partner/rules.html:225
msgid ""
"We reserve the right to revoke embed access (by removing your domain from "
"our allowlist) if these rules are violated. Violations will be addressed "
"through:"
